<doxygen xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="compound.xsd" version="1.9.8" xml:lang="en-US">
  <compounddef id="group__structs__module" kind="group">
    <compoundname>structs_module</compoundname>
    <title>Structs Module</title>
    <briefdescription>
<para>Core data structures and type definitions. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<sect1 id="group__structs__module_1structs_overview">
<title>Overview</title>
<para>The Structs module contains fundamental data structures used throughout the framework.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__structs__module_1structs_types">
<title>Types</title>
<para>Key structures include:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>settings_t: Analysis configuration</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>event_t: Event data container</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>graph_t: <ref refid="classGraph" kindref="compound">Graph</ref> data structure (see <ref refid="group__graph__module" kindref="compound">Graph Module</ref>)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>folds_t: K-fold cross-validation data</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>optimizer_params_t: Optimizer configuration</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>model_report: Training progress reports</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="group__structs__module_1structs_property_mod">
<title>Property System</title>
<para>The module includes a property system (<computeroutput>cproperty</computeroutput>) for:</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Type-safe getters and setters</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Lazy evaluation</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Python binding support </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
    </detaileddescription>
  </compounddef>
</doxygen>
